{"tid":2122393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：潘小濤8.7告別晴朗  疑與續牌有關 商台︰經多番挽留 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-07-24T03:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T03:30:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b53308caeaf6a59899d32bfb4e53f0a3c5798263","tid":2122393,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/UI6JZYYVLACNQMUQYLB3NLCOKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FUI6JZYYVLACNQMUQYLB3NLCOKU%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6LktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=6cf7a167\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FUI6JZYYVLACNQMUQYLB3NLCOKU%2F&h=edc6b3e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/UI6JZYYVLACNQMUQYLB3NLCOKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：潘小濤8.7告別晴朗 <br />\n疑與續牌有關 商台︰經多番挽留 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GnSBSNXBgZa9wG_-rn3OVdmEQWc=/1000x839/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7S3RPGJH25HVXAAZ4QLFDZXGQQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGnSBSNXBgZa9wG_-rn3OVdmEQWc%3D%2F1000x839%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7S3RPGJH25HVXAAZ4QLFDZXGQQ.gif&h=129bc8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提起商台903《在晴朗的一天出發》，。。。。。。。。。之後會以嘉賓身份主持部份雷霆881節目。<br />\n<br />\n將以嘉賓身份客串881節目<br />\n<br />\n903《晴朗》由林海峰、小濤同KY阮子健主持，三個主持老友鬼鬼，噚日開咪就搵小濤開刀，小濤話「《晴朗》冇咗我係一個損失」，林海峰笑返佢轉頭，「知唔知點解領事館要撤走，因為噚晚收到潘小濤唔做商台，佢就燒咗啲文件，見佢份合約冇用燒晒佢」。八方聽到笑到肚痛，不過小濤冇喺節目交代離職原因，預告last day先同大家交代。<br />\n<br />\n坊間對小濤離職有唔少揣測，聯想會唔會同國安法有關。八方聽聞，商台2016年雖然獲政府續牌至2028年，不過就會喺2022年8月做中期檢討，而商台喺逆權運動期間收到好多投訴信，壓力唔細。商台回覆話，經多番挽留同商討。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}